{"tid":488843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女導遊尖東遭中國遊客圍毆 警拉3遊客","createTime":"2017-12-04T06:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T06:58:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8d430ea1d8235024b7bb516adb65c0cd8be2f837","tid":488843,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T06:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171204/large/1512364555_c1db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171204%2Flarge%2F1512364555_c1db.jpg&h=8f12a065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀加連威老道100號港晶中心，上午11時半，兩個由湖南來港的旅行團，被安排在上址購物，期間，其中一團的團友，疑因事與女導遊發生爭執，該名女導遊報稱被3名遊客圍毆。警方接報到場將她送院檢驗，並拘捕3名涉案男遊客。<br />\n<br />\n約半小時後，另一團的一名內地男遊客，離開店舖時，突遭人叉頸襲擊而感到不適，獲送院檢驗。他向警方報稱，懷疑因拒絕購物而遭人施襲。<br />\n<br />\n其後旅行社改派職員到場，兩旅行團繼續行程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171204/57538800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171204%2F57538800&d=GG%2F5oLso5SoFJp87e8hPmZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=63d485b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171204%2F57538800&h=071c0030\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171204/57538800</a>"},{"pid":"ba8177371a61512732a18cbabef6fa801169371c","tid":488843,"uid":30640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T06:10:49.000Z","msg":"湖南土匪"},{"pid":"464805ef023d8a9b0f5fc41904e63041eaf910f5","tid":488843,"uid":61832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"支那小學雞排隊"},{"pid":"050f77832b1ef0df4dc4d8d1d85063f731db1b87","tid":488843,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T06:31:10.000Z","msg":"又係d搏懵旅客黑旅團引發既事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" cl